    "gousto_id": "13482",
    "description": "Treat your mum to a finale she won't forget. You'll pile cinnamon apples onto pastry, bake with pecans till golden, then drizzle with homemade salted caramel and maple cr\u00e8me fra\u00eeche. Flipping delicious.",
    "cuisine": "French",
